# Write your MySQL query statement below
select x,y,z, (case when x+y>z and x+z>y and z+y>x then 'Yes' else 'No' end) triangle
from triangle;


In math, three line segments can form a triangle only if sum of any of two segments is greater than the third one. 
(in other words, the subtraction of any of two segments is smaller than the third one)
